{"results":[{"aya":"029","id":3817,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"那些人说：不然！你们自己原来不是信道者，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"030","id":3818,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"我们对你们绝无权力。不然！你们是悖逆的民众。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"031","id":3819,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"故我们应当受我们的主的判决，我们确是尝试的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"032","id":3820,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"所以我们使你们迷误，我们自己也确是迷误的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"033","id":3821,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"在那日，他们必定同受刑罚。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"034","id":3822,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"我必定这样对待犯罪者。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"035","id":3823,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"他们确是这样的：有人对他们说：除真主外，绝无应受崇拜的，他们就妄自尊大，","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":26,"previousPage":"/zh/s037-4.json","nextPage":"/zh/s037-6.json"}}